thread.title: Miss Jacquie Gibson
thread.title_full: Not Socks reviewed by Miss Jacquie Gibson

author: Miss Jacquie Gibson
title: Miss Jacquie Gibson
text:
I live in England & sent out to NZ Christmas presents for my niece & nephew. I couldn't have asked for a better service! From the quality of the products, the speed in the delivery, the site being so easy to use. The best bit though was the hand written note on the parcel!
I've now told all my family in England about you & they either have or will be using you in future!!
